# Core BEM Modules

## Main Modules
- [bem/__init__.py](mdc:bem/__init__.py): Package initialization and exports
- [bem/electrostatics.py](mdc:bem/electrostatics.py): Core electrostatics simulation functionality
- [bem/fastlap_wrapper.py](mdc:bem/fastlap_wrapper.py): Interface to the FastLap BEM implementation
- [bem/grid.py](mdc:bem/grid.py): Grid generation for simulation domains
- [bem/pipeline.py](mdc:bem/pipeline.py): BEM simulation pipeline
- [bem/triangulation.py](mdc:bem/triangulation.py): Mesh triangulation utilities
- [bem/show_result.py](mdc:bem/show_result.py): Result visualization tools
- [bem/spherical_harmonics.py](mdc:bem/spherical_harmonics.py): Spherical harmonics calculations

## Mesh Handling
The package uses triangular meshes to represent surfaces, with various utilities for mesh creation, manipulation, and refinement.
